All Implemented Interfaces:
EventServer
public class M_MUL
extends M_ADD

Upon the occurrence of an event at the REQ input, an instance of this function block type performs MATRIX multiplication of the IN1 and IN2 inputs. The result is placed in the OUT output, and the size of the output matrix is automatically adjusted to hold the result.

See M_ADD for documentation of the service sequences for this function block type.

See the TEST_MATRIX system configuration for an example of the use of an instance of this class.
